                     <interp inst="t17861025-65-person853" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            ."</p>
               <p>P. S.</p>
               <p>"Be sure to send me word when</p>
               <p>"you receive this, as soon as ever you</p>
               <p>"can; I will not send the will and power</p>
               <p>"before you send me an answer."</p>
               <p>Adressed to Mrs. 
               <persName id="t17861025-65-person854">
