                     <interp inst="t17861025-65-person871" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            ? - Very well, have known him many years; I saw him write many times. (The will shewn him.) I do not think this is his handwriting.</p>
               <p>Did you ever know him spell his name with an I? - No.</p>
               <p>Mr. Sheridan. Did you ever know him spell his name with an S. - No, never; he always spelt his name Druce.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17861025-65-person872">
                  ELIZABETH
                   WELLS
               <interp inst="t17861025-65-person872" type="surname" value="WELLS"></interp>
