                     <interp inst="t17861025-65-person873" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            ; I have seen him write. (Looks at the will.) I do not think this is his hand-writing; I knew him when he was in his apprenticeship; have seen him write in his shop-book.</p>
               <p>Look at that, and see whether that is his hand-writing or not? - I think it is.</p>
               <p>How is it spelt? - I know how he used to spell Druce.</p>
               <p>How is that spelt? - That is not spelt as he spells his name now.</p>
               <p>(Shews her a letter spelt Duce.)</p>
